::Zardus::

Zardus's eyes nearly widen at Feline's transmission, the Alliance
commander not replying. Silence was as good as permission.



--- In nbwrpg@y..., logomorph@h... wrote:
> Feline::
> She sighed as she got the quardinants. She opened her link to 
> Zardus. "Yo, Zardus babe. I Got to go and meet an old friend. I'll 
> give you the details later on. Bye for now Bot Babe."
> 
> She transformed into panther mode and ran to the hanger.  She got a 
> small shuttle and fired up the engines.  She headed out of the hanger 
> bay and straight for the meeting place.  She couldn't wait.
> 
> 
> KitKat3::
> She smiled and awaited the decision. "And if all goes well, the 
> maximals will be crushed and on to the Alll..." The program ran it's 
> course," Zardus is my commander and I shall obey only him." she 
> muttered under her breath.  She looked at Drillbit and the 
> other. "Let's get the maximals" she said in a low voice. 
> 
> 
> --- In nbwrpg@y..., RoboRick007 <rfa007@h...> wrote:
> > ::DrillBit::
> > 
> > "Ok. I'll ask DarkFate and Kill about the attack now."
> > He walks back into the room.
> > "Dark, Kill, you guys want to attack the CF?"
> > 
> > ::Hot Rod::
> > 
> > He sent the location.(I dont really care where) 
> > "I'll meet you there asap."
> > He ran out of the CF, transformed, and drove towards the location.
